TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_107

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_111

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_113

TranslationLabels.Text: But to summarize, I recently started working for my father's second wife, after he unexpectedly passed away.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_130

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_131
TranslationLabels.Text: And I'm only just starting to get to know them.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_132
TranslationLabels.Text: But they seem like nice, smart girls.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_133
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's put my theory to the test.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_135

TranslationLabels.Label: l_100_130_1_136
TranslationLabels.Text: So as far as I can-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_121_118
TranslationLabels.Text: *Whisper* But that means you can't do anything that would get me in trouble with [REL_M4].

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_200_3
TranslationLabels.Text: Its so cool that I have a [REL_B2] now!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_200_73
TranslationLabels.Text: You know, with what happened to [REL_F4] and all...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_900_3
TranslationLabels.Text: Of course! I can't keep my [REL_S2] waiting, now can I?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_900_22
TranslationLabels.Text: (Its really cute that shes so excited about having a [REL_B2].)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_900_107
TranslationLabels.Text: You're pretty good at this [REL_B2] thing.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_901_32
TranslationLabels.Text: Hes probably just some driver her mentor hired for her little princess.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_2_903_9
TranslationLabels.Text: (She gets out of the car and goes inside the mansion.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_d_6
TranslationLabels.Text: She has been in the employ of the [REL_FAM] for many years, and seems to genuinely care for Madeline and the girls.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_6_r_1
TranslationLabels.Text: I'm keeping my eye on him. I'm not going to let him hurt the girls.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_4_r_1
TranslationLabels.Text: There's no way that asshole is who he says he is!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_4_104_29
TranslationLabels.Text: I wonder how [REL_M2] will feel about that...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_4_104_30
TranslationLabels.Text: About what? Her [REL_D1] acting like a spoiled brat that is too lazy to get her own drink?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_4_902_51
TranslationLabels.Text: It means she won't be coming back to your sorry ass anymore.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_4_910_9
TranslationLabels.Text: (She gets out without saying a word.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_15
TranslationLabels.Text: Don't bother. The door to the disc-

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_23
TranslationLabels.Text: You are not to interfere in any [REL_FM].

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_mouse_interactions_1
TranslationLabels.Text:
During dialogs, a <highlight>mouse interaction</highlight> may appear.
When the mouse interaction icon pops up, move your mouse as indicated by the animation to advance the scene.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_mouse_interactions_2
TranslationLabels.Text: But make sure you complete the interactions before the <highlight>timer</highlight> runs out, or there may be consequences!

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_dialog_choices_1
TranslationLabels.Text: During dialogs, you may be presented with multiple <highlight>choices</highlight> on how to respond.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_dialog_choices_2
TranslationLabels.Text: It is important to choose wisely, as your reaction may affect the outcome of the dialog as well as your <highlight>relationship</highlight> with the person you are talking to.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_dialog_choices_3
TranslationLabels.Text: Some choices will remain locked until specific conditions are met.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_character_stats_1
TranslationLabels.Text:
Each of the main girls has the following two stats:
<highlight>love</highlight> and <highlight>lust</highlight>.

These stats reflect your current <highlight>relationship</highlight> with them.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_character_stats_2
TranslationLabels.Text:
You can increase their stats by making the right choices during dialogs and gaining their approval.

Be careful, if you say or do something a character doesn't approve of, her stats will decrease.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_map_1
TranslationLabels.Text:
[180|715|-375]You can use the <highlight>navigation arrows</highlight> on screen to move around.
However, if you want to save some time, you can also use the <highlight>map</highlight>.

This allows you to easily travel to different locations.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_map_2
TranslationLabels.Text: [180|715|-375]Go ahead and open the map, and select your apartment on the city tab.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_dialog_topics_1
TranslationLabels.Text:
During some dialogs, you will be presented with multiple <highlight>topics</highlight>.
Talking about certain topics can help you increase your relationship with that character.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_dialog_topics_2
TranslationLabels.Text:
You can pick up to 3 topics to talk about, before the conversation ends.

If you want to end it before that, click the X on the top right of the screen.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_dialog_topics_3
TranslationLabels.Text:
When they have nothing new to say about a topic, it will be grayed out.

But remember to check back every now and then, as the story progresses characters may offer you important new information.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_spy_intro_1
TranslationLabels.Text: You have unlocked the option to spy on the girls using the hidden corridors.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_spy_travel_1
TranslationLabels.Text: Click on any of the spy icons to travel directly to the corresponding air vent.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_spy_travel_2
TranslationLabels.Text: This will allow you to spy on the selected room.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_spy_travel_3
TranslationLabels.Text: Spying on the girls at specific times will unlock new content and progress the main story.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_spy_travel_4
TranslationLabels.Text: Rememer to keep an eye on the hints if you ever need help.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_fights_1
TranslationLabels.Text:
During fights, arrow icons will move down the middle of the screen.
Press the corresponding arrow on your keyboard when the icon is in the highlighted area to hit your opponent.

But be careful, if you fail to press the correct key at the right time, your opponent will hit you instead.

TranslationLabels.Label: tc_fights_2
TranslationLabels.Text:
If you press the key when the arrow is in the center of the highligted area, you will score a perfect hit and your combo counter will increase.
The higher your combo is, the more damage you will deal with each hit.

Take down your opponent by scoring big combos and avoid getting hit!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_d_3
TranslationLabels.Text: Annabelle seems to be a very timid girl. But maybe you just need to get to know her a bit better...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_1
TranslationLabels.Text: She takes her showers in the morning. I have to make sure I'll be in the upstairs bathroom before she gets there.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_2
TranslationLabels.Text: I need to take her to her art classes on Friday at 19:00.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_3
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe I can find out a bit more about her by talking to one of the other girls?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_4
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe one of the girls has a spare laptop I could borrow?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_5
TranslationLabels.Text: I saw her going into the study, carrying an old book.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_6
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe I should focus on the other girls for now?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_7
TranslationLabels.Text: She works out late in the afternoon.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_8
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe I should join the girls for dinner?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_9
TranslationLabels.Text: Olivia promised me she would leave her laptop in my room.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_10
TranslationLabels.Text: I should try installing Hentai Impact on the laptop.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_11
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe I can find a way to get into her room when Kate is cleaning it?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_13
TranslationLabels.Text: Do you really want me to spell it out? Use the toilet roll on the toilet!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_14
TranslationLabels.Text: I need to take her to her art classes again, on Friday at 19:00.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_15
TranslationLabels.Text: I could spy on her when she takes her morning bath.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_16
TranslationLabels.Text: I promised Madeline I would help Annabelle with her workout.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_17
TranslationLabels.Text: I need to wait for Olivia to tell me what she wants in return for the laptop.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_18
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe I should focus on Olivia for a bit.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_19
TranslationLabels.Text: If she doesn't feel like working out, I should cut her some slack.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_20
TranslationLabels.Text: I should cover for her during dinner.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_21
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe I shouldn't lie for her during dinner.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_h_22
TranslationLabels.Text: I should spy on her and Madeline at midnight.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_r_1
TranslationLabels.Text: I hope he doesn't talk to me.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_r_2
TranslationLabels.Text: At least he seems to be friendly.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_7
TranslationLabels.Text: (But I guess that was the point.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_10
TranslationLabels.Text: (You put the towel over your head just like you did with Olivia.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_17
TranslationLabels.Text: T-The door was open! I...I thought-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_19
TranslationLabels.Text: (She runs out of the bathroom and quickly closes the door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_24
TranslationLabels.Text: (But I feel like an asshole for doing that to her.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_26
TranslationLabels.Text: (You put your clothes back on and leave the bathroom.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_27
TranslationLabels.Text: (As you walk past Annabelle's bedroom, you hear a sound coming from inside.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_29
TranslationLabels.Text: (Crap! I didn't think she'd be that upset...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_30
TranslationLabels.Text: (You press your ear against the door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_36
TranslationLabels.Text: (So, the shy girl has a naughty side as well...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_1_38
TranslationLabels.Text: (Anyway, I better get out of here, before someone sees me.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_101_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (She blushes and avoids making eye contact with you.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_101_5
TranslationLabels.Text: So, any big plans for today?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_101_9
TranslationLabels.Text: (She seems uncomfortable talking to you, so you decide to leave her alone.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_102_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (She seems to be focused on her studies.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_102_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (I shouldn't be bothering her right now.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Annabelle is staring dreamily into the distance.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (She startles, snapping out of her thoughts.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_4
TranslationLabels.Text: Oh! Uhm, no, I was just...thinking.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_5
TranslationLabels.Text: Oh, my bad. I didn't mean to interrupt you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_8
TranslationLabels.Text: Well, Ill leave you to it then.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_11
TranslationLabels.Text: (You notice a familiar looking book under Annabelle's arm.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_12
TranslationLabels.Text: (Is that...one of the books of sin?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_16
TranslationLabels.Text: Hey Annabelle, sorry to bother you...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_17
TranslationLabels.Text: But I noticed that book you have there.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_21
TranslationLabels.Text: Yeah. I was wondering if I could maybe borrow it?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_22
TranslationLabels.Text: If it's not too much trouble?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_26
TranslationLabels.Text: (Don't tell me she actually reads this stuff?!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_103_31
TranslationLabels.Text: (Great! I'm one step closer to finding out what that bookcase is hiding.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_104_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Annabelle is so focused on her painting that she doesnt even notice you.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_104_8
TranslationLabels.Text: (She clearly isn't comfortable with you watching her paint.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (But her gaze wanders as she just sits on the bench, not actively exercising.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (As soon as she sees you, she suddenly starts working out.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_7
TranslationLabels.Text: (Knowing she is obviously faking it, you suppress a smile.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_16
TranslationLabels.Text: Hey, would you like to work out together?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_19
TranslationLabels.Text: It looks like you just started, so I might as well join you, right?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_22
TranslationLabels.Text: Cool. Let me get changed and I'll be back in 5 minutes.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_28
TranslationLabels.Text: Actually, I'm feeling a bit sore today...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_32
TranslationLabels.Text: We can work out together some other time.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_35
TranslationLabels.Text: That's all part of the process, Annabelle.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_36
TranslationLabels.Text: But you have to push through if you want to see the results.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_39
TranslationLabels.Text: All right then. I'll go get changed.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_44
TranslationLabels.Text: Let's get those muscles nice and warm.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_45
TranslationLabels.Text: A good warm-up will help to prevent injuries.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_46
TranslationLabels.Text: So make sure never to skip it.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_49
TranslationLabels.Text: (To get your heart rate up a bit.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_50
TranslationLabels.Text: (Then you do some sit-ups with her...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_58
TranslationLabels.Text: Come on, you can do it!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_59
TranslationLabels.Text: (After that you focus on her back muscles...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_63
TranslationLabels.Text: Exhale when you pull the weight down.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_84
TranslationLabels.Text: (Suddenly, you realize you're not only staring at her boobs, but you stopped talking as well...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_86
TranslationLabels.Text: (You feel your cheeks flush and quickly meet her eyes.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_87
TranslationLabels.Text: (It looks like she didn't notice you staring...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_88
TranslationLabels.Text: (For a brief moment, you see a slight smile on her face.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_98
TranslationLabels.Text: I really appreciate you helping me out like this...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_105_99
TranslationLabels.Text: Don't mention it, it's my pleasure!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_5
TranslationLabels.Text: At first, the thought of having a [REL_B1] made me a bit...nervous.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_6
TranslationLabels.Text: But now that I'm getting to know you better, I really like it.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_8
TranslationLabels.Text: And I'm glad I got to know you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_10
TranslationLabels.Text: We don't really spend a lot of time together...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_14
TranslationLabels.Text: There isn't much to tell you...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_21
TranslationLabels.Text: I think it's so cool when someone is artistic.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_24
TranslationLabels.Text: I can't even draw a decent stick figure...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_26
TranslationLabels.Text: And who doesn't love video games?!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_27
TranslationLabels.Text: Life would be so boring without them.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_29
TranslationLabels.Text: Uhm...I don't think she really likes me...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_31
TranslationLabels.Text: Well, she doesn't really talk to me a lot...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_32
TranslationLabels.Text: Maybe it's because we are so unalike?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_33
TranslationLabels.Text: She works out a lot and she's very active on social media.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_34
TranslationLabels.Text: And she's super confident...she loves posting selfies...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_38
TranslationLabels.Text: I admire her a lot, she's so smart and successful...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_39
TranslationLabels.Text: And she's teaching us how to be like her.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_40
TranslationLabels.Text: She's also very supportive of my art!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_41
TranslationLabels.Text: Of course, she can be a bit strict sometimes...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_42
TranslationLabels.Text: But that's just for our own benefit.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_44
TranslationLabels.Text: All he ever cared about was his company...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_46
TranslationLabels.Text: I know it's her job, but she always looks after us.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_47
TranslationLabels.Text: And I think she likes it too.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_48
TranslationLabels.Text: I don't really know her yet.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_200_49
TranslationLabels.Text: She only started working here one day before you came.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (It will probably take me a few hours to get everything set up.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_2_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (I don't have time for that right now.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (All right, let's see if I can if get this to work...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_5
TranslationLabels.Text: (Yes! I actually got it to run!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_6
TranslationLabels.Text: (Now, let's see what this game is all about...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_14
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm, there's a human, an orc and a demon.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_15
TranslationLabels.Text: (Oh, apparently you can unlock more avatar choices in their shop.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_16
TranslationLabels.Text: (I guess that explains how they make money...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_21
TranslationLabels.Text: But first, we'll show you a quick tutorial so you can learn the basics.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_26
TranslationLabels.Text: (It's a lot bigger than I expected...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_27
TranslationLabels.Text: (How am I ever going to find Annabelle?!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_28
TranslationLabels.Text: (I have no idea where to go...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_29
TranslationLabels.Text: (And there's no point in running around aimlessly.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_30
TranslationLabels.Text: (Besides, this took up way too much of my time already.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_32
TranslationLabels.Text: (I need to find out what Annabelle's character is called.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_33
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe I can sneak into her room and have a look, when she's not around?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_300_34
TranslationLabels.Text: (I guess it will have to wait.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_301_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Before I can continue playing, I need to find out what Annabelle's character is called.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_301_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe I can sneak into her room and have a look, when she's not around?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_400_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Oh! Annabelle is taking her morning bath...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_400_7
TranslationLabels.Text: (You have unlocked Annabelle's naked paperdoll animation.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_400_8
TranslationLabels.Text: (She leans back with a sigh and closes her eyes...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_400_12
TranslationLabels.Text: (Anyway, I shouldn't stay in here too long.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_400_13
TranslationLabels.Text: (I don't want to risk getting caught.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_400_14
TranslationLabels.Text: (You leave the corridor and return to the utility closet.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (Madeline is standing in front of some kind of wooden contraption.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_7
TranslationLabels.Text: Now, what should I do with you?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_8
TranslationLabels.Text: I think I deserve to be punished...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_10
TranslationLabels.Text: And what kind of punishment would be fitting, in your opinion?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_14
TranslationLabels.Text: Oh? You think you have been that bad, have you?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_16
TranslationLabels.Text: I should know better than lying to you, [REL_M3].

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_18
TranslationLabels.Text: (Madeline walks over to a rack filled with straps and paddles.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_20
TranslationLabels.Text: (She carefully examines each item hanging on the rack, her gaze lingering thoughtfully on each one.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_22
TranslationLabels.Text: (She looks so hot in that leather outfit...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_23
TranslationLabels.Text: Yes, this one will do nicely.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_24
TranslationLabels.Text: (She removes one of the leather paddles)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_27
TranslationLabels.Text: I have picked the perfect tool for your punishment.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_28
TranslationLabels.Text: (She presses the paddle against Annabelle's chin.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_31
TranslationLabels.Text: (She forces Annabelle's head up with the paddle.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_32
TranslationLabels.Text: Look at me when I am talking to you!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_34
TranslationLabels.Text: *Scoffs* It seems I have to teach you some manners as well.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_36
TranslationLabels.Text: (Madeline walks around to the other side of the contraption.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_37
TranslationLabels.Text: Let this be a lesson to you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_39
TranslationLabels.Text: (And forcefully slaps Annabelle's ass with it.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_47
TranslationLabels.Text: (After a while, Madeline stops spanking Annabelle...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_48
TranslationLabels.Text: That will be enough for today.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_49
TranslationLabels.Text: I trust you will improve your behavior?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_53
TranslationLabels.Text: Now, let's get you out of this.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_54
TranslationLabels.Text: (I'll get back to my room before they leave...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_62
TranslationLabels.Text: (And kind of hot...if I'm being honest.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_63
TranslationLabels.Text: (It feels wrong, but I can't help but being turned on by what I just saw...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_65
TranslationLabels.Text: (And somehow knowing that I played a part in them being punished...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_66
TranslationLabels.Text: (It just turns me on even more.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_68
TranslationLabels.Text: (This doesn't even come close to normal.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_71
TranslationLabels.Text: (And Annabelle seemed a bit turned on as well, if anything.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_72
TranslationLabels.Text: (Wait...is that why she lied during dinner?!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_75
TranslationLabels.Text: (There's definitely something strange going on here.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_401_76
TranslationLabels.Text: (And I really don't know what to make of all this...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_6
TranslationLabels.Text: Are you ready to go to your art class?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_14
TranslationLabels.Text: (Come to think of it, she's hardly said more than a few words to me since we've met.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_15
TranslationLabels.Text: (She just stays locked up in her room most of the time.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_17
TranslationLabels.Text: (I can imagine she's upset and would rather be alone.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_19
TranslationLabels.Text: (Of course, seeing me naked probably didn't help much either...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_20
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's see if I can get her to open up a bit.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_21
TranslationLabels.Text: Are you looking forward to going to art class again?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_24
TranslationLabels.Text: Did you forget I was taking you?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_26
TranslationLabels.Text: You seemed a bit surprised earlier...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_27
TranslationLabels.Text: When I came to pick you up?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_30
TranslationLabels.Text: I guess I lost track of time...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_36
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe I should just give it some time.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_37
TranslationLabels.Text: (I'm sure she'll open up once she gets to know me a bit better.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_43
TranslationLabels.Text: All right then. I'll be waiting here.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_44
TranslationLabels.Text: Let me get the door for you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_47
TranslationLabels.Text: (She should be out any minute now.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_51
TranslationLabels.Text: (As she comes down the stairs you can't help but admire her curvy body.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_63
TranslationLabels.Text: Great! Let's get you home then.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_66
TranslationLabels.Text: (Or is she this quiet with everyone?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_67
TranslationLabels.Text: So, how was your art class?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_3_900_70
TranslationLabels.Text: (You echo her silence in an attempt to get more out of her.)

TranslationLabels.Text: (It seems I can't even get shit-faced in peace.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_66
TranslationLabels.Text: (You get up and walk towards the door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_67
TranslationLabels.Text: (But as soon as you open it, a giant of a man forces his way in and points a gun at you.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_71
TranslationLabels.Text: (As you step back, he enters your apartment.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_74
TranslationLabels.Text: Look, I already told him...I just need a little more time.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_75
TranslationLabels.Text: Time's up. Either you pay right now...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_76
TranslationLabels.Text: (He menacingly points his gun at you.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_77
TranslationLabels.Text: Or I put a hole in you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_78
TranslationLabels.Text: (Little does he know that this is hardly the first time someone has pointed a gun at you.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_79
TranslationLabels.Text: (The countless hours of training make your body react almost instinctively.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_80
TranslationLabels.Text: (In one fluid motion, you move your head out of the line of fire, firmly grab the gun with your left hand...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_86
TranslationLabels.Text: (And smash the side of your right hand into his wrist to disarm him.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_90
TranslationLabels.Text: I wasn't going to shoot you...I swear!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_91
TranslationLabels.Text: Tell Ruslan he will get his money.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_92
TranslationLabels.Text: He will just have to be patient a bit longer.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_93
TranslationLabels.Text: Ruslan is not known for his patience.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_94
TranslationLabels.Text: I don't give a shit. Now get the fuck out of my apartment!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_96
TranslationLabels.Text: Next time he will just send more-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_102
TranslationLabels.Text: (As if I didn't have enough on my mind already.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_103
TranslationLabels.Text: (You drop down onto your couch with a throbbing headache.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_104
TranslationLabels.Text: (It seemed like a good idea at the time...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_106
TranslationLabels.Text: (A friend hooked you up with Ruslan, a local "investor".)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_107
TranslationLabels.Text: (I never should have taken his money...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_108
TranslationLabels.Text: (But I was so sure my business would be a success.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_112
TranslationLabels.Text: (Soon, you had to fire your staff and sell off all your equipment.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_116
TranslationLabels.Text: (And you can't help but ask yourself...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_117
TranslationLabels.Text: (How am I ever going to get myself out of this mess?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_118
TranslationLabels.Text: (You notice that you are still holding the gun in your hand.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_122
TranslationLabels.Text: (Then again, it's not like all my problems are going to just magically-)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_134
TranslationLabels.Text: (This might be just the break I was waiting for!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_135
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe there is still a chance to fix this mess I'm in after all.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_137
TranslationLabels.Text: (You arrive at the address you were given, and find yourself in front of a big gate.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_141
TranslationLabels.Text: (Before you can finish your thought, the gates swing open.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_143
TranslationLabels.Text: (You pull up their driveway and notice a police car with two cops inside parked out front.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_145
TranslationLabels.Text: (Looks like this place is under surveillance...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_146
TranslationLabels.Text: (You get out and walk up to the front door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_147
TranslationLabels.Text: (But before you can ring the bell, a beautiful woman wearing a maid uniform opens the door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_149
TranslationLabels.Text: Yes, that's right. Nice to meet-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_152
TranslationLabels.Text: (You follow her into what looks like a study, where she asks you to take a seat.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_153
TranslationLabels.Text: Miss Caine will be with you shortly.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_156
TranslationLabels.Text: (She leaves before you can finish your sentence.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_157
TranslationLabels.Text: (Someone got up on the wrong side of bed this morning.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_159
TranslationLabels.Text: (Miss Caine sure is taking her time...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_161
TranslationLabels.Text: (I wonder what line of work she's in, this mansion is huge.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_165
TranslationLabels.Text: (Wait, isn't that the woman I saw at the police station yesterday?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_167
TranslationLabels.Text: (You get up from your seat to introduce yourself.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_168
TranslationLabels.Text: Yes. It's nice to meet you, Miss-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_170
TranslationLabels.Text: (She makes it sound more like a command than a question.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_172
TranslationLabels.Text: (You follow her inside her office where you both sit down at her desk.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_173
TranslationLabels.Text: My name is Madeline Caine. Thank you for coming, Mister Bishop.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_174
TranslationLabels.Text: It's my pleasure, Miss Caine. But please, call me [NAME_1].

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_176
TranslationLabels.Text: (You notice she doesn't extend you the same courtesy.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_177
TranslationLabels.Text: I'll get straight to the point. My husband was recently murdered.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_178
TranslationLabels.Text: (She looks at you, waiting for a reaction.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_180
TranslationLabels.Text: (She responds with a hint of coldness in her voice.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_182
TranslationLabels.Text: Due to the circumstances surrounding his death, we are currently not allowed to leave the house without a police escort.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_185
TranslationLabels.Text: Yesterday, while discussing this with Detective Higgins, I expressed that we felt safe within the mansion and don't require protection.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_187
TranslationLabels.Text: Even though he doesn't believe we are at risk, it is standard security protocol to be under supervision.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_188
TranslationLabels.Text: He suggested I hire a private security company if I'm unhappy with the current situation.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_192
TranslationLabels.Text: Imagine my surprise, when I found out my late husband had a son, whom he neglected to mention in nearly 25 years of marriage!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_193
TranslationLabels.Text: Hold on a moment! Are you implying that you are...my stepmother?!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_195
TranslationLabels.Text: That appears to be the case, yes.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_196
TranslationLabels.Text: (Is she for real?! I guess its not a surprise my father remarried...but still, this is not what I was expecting...at all!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_197
TranslationLabels.Text: Judging from the expression on your face, you were not aware of our existence either?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_203
TranslationLabels.Text: (Was that a hint of annoyance in her voice?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_208
TranslationLabels.Text: (You feel like your whole world has just been turned upside down.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_209
TranslationLabels.Text: I understand this is a lot to take in.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_211
TranslationLabels.Text: However, I would like to offer you a job, nonetheless.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_214
TranslationLabels.Text: Other than that you are free to do as you please, so long as you are available when I call on you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_215
TranslationLabels.Text: Of course, this also means that you would have to stay at the mansion until this whole thing blows over.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_216
TranslationLabels.Text: I-I dont know....I think I need some time to process all of this.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_217
TranslationLabels.Text: Besides, as a professional bodyguard, it would be unethical to accept a contract protecting a relative or someone with whom I have any personal relationship.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_219
TranslationLabels.Text: I understand that. And I appreciate your professionalism.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_220
TranslationLabels.Text: However, I am sure you can make an exception in this case.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_221
TranslationLabels.Text: The only reason I want to hire you is to keep Detective Higgins off my back.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_222
TranslationLabels.Text: It will most likely be the easiest job you have ever had.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_224
TranslationLabels.Text: (Again, her expression changes, but you can't quite read if it's anger, annoyance or something else.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_225
TranslationLabels.Text: Im sorry. I just dont think-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_226
TranslationLabels.Text: I will pay you $100,000. Half up front, half once my husbands murder investigation is closed.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_228
TranslationLabels.Text: (That would be more than enough to pay off my debt with Ruslan!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_229
TranslationLabels.Text: (Besides, where am I going to stay after I get evicted?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_231
TranslationLabels.Text: (You struggle to keep a straight face.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_232
TranslationLabels.Text: That is a...substantial amount of money.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_233
TranslationLabels.Text: So, do we have an agreement then?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_234
TranslationLabels.Text: (There is no way I could ever turn down an offer like this.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_240
TranslationLabels.Text: (I knew it sounded too good to be true.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_242
TranslationLabels.Text: As you can understand, they are going through a difficult period right now.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_244
TranslationLabels.Text: Not being able to leave the mansion only adds to their frustration.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_245
TranslationLabels.Text: Getting us to our appointments <highlight>on time</highlight> is your priority.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_246
TranslationLabels.Text: If you fail to do that, I will have no choice but to fire you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_251
TranslationLabels.Text: Failure to do so will result in immediate termination.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_252
TranslationLabels.Text: (That's an unusual condition, but I can respect their privacy.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_254
TranslationLabels.Text: And finally, if you make my girls feel uncomfortable, in any way, I will fire you without hesitation.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_256
TranslationLabels.Text: (I cant agree to that, can I?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_259
TranslationLabels.Text: (Its not like I have anything to lose...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_260
TranslationLabels.Text: (In fact, this may be my only chance to get out of the mess I'm in...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_262
TranslationLabels.Text: Outstanding. I knew we would be able to reach an agreement.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_264
TranslationLabels.Text: (The door opens and the woman that let you in earlier, enters the room.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_265
TranslationLabels.Text: (Her eyes briefly flicker in your direction.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_267
TranslationLabels.Text: Would you please fetch the girls for me?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_271
TranslationLabels.Text: (I can imagine it must have been quite a shock to them as well.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_272
TranslationLabels.Text: I hope they took the news well?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_273
TranslationLabels.Text: As well as can be expected.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_274
TranslationLabels.Text: (I'm not sure what that's supposed to mean.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_275
TranslationLabels.Text: (There is a knock at the door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_277
TranslationLabels.Text: (Three beautiful young women enter the room.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_278
TranslationLabels.Text: Girls, this is [NAME_1]. As I told you earlier, he will be staying with us for a while to ensure our safety.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_279
TranslationLabels.Text: (Earlier? She must have been very confident I would take the job.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_283
TranslationLabels.Text: It seems so. Im still processing it myself.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_286
TranslationLabels.Text: I cant wait to get to know you!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_287
TranslationLabels.Text: (Her excitement is contagious, and you can't help but smile.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_288
TranslationLabels.Text: I look forward to that as well, Olivia.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_289
TranslationLabels.Text: And this is Annabelle, my middle [REL_D1].

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_291
TranslationLabels.Text: *Softly* Uhm, its a pleasure to meet you.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_292
TranslationLabels.Text: (Annabelle's greeting is shy and reserved. She seems hesitant, but there's a glimmer of curiosity in her eyes.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_293
TranslationLabels.Text: It's nice to meet you too, Annabelle.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_294
TranslationLabels.Text: Lastly, this is Victoria, my eldest [REL_D1].

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_298
TranslationLabels.Text: Seriously, [REL_M2]? John is killed, and suddenly a stranger shows up claiming to be his son.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_299
TranslationLabels.Text: (She calls her father by his first name? That's interesting.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_301
TranslationLabels.Text: Dont you think this is all a bit too much of a coincidence?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_303
TranslationLabels.Text: But, [REL_M2]...cant you see hes just after our money? Please tell me you dont believe-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_305
TranslationLabels.Text: (Madeline's hand slams down on her desk, startling everyone in the room.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_307
TranslationLabels.Text: (The three girls instantly lower their heads and nervously study the floor.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_308
TranslationLabels.Text: (Madelines voice drops back to her calm, though stern tone and she continues as if nothing happened.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_309
TranslationLabels.Text: I know you girls are frustrated with being locked up inside the house and having the cops around all the time.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_310
TranslationLabels.Text: But now that [NAME_1] is here, the police will leave us alone.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_311
TranslationLabels.Text: I have also asked him to escort each of you to your weekly club practice.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_312
TranslationLabels.Text: Ooh! Does that mean I can go to swimming practice again?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_316
TranslationLabels.Text: Is there anything you would like to add, Victoria?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_319
TranslationLabels.Text: Nevertheless, I will see you downstairs later.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_325
TranslationLabels.Text: That will be all, girls. Off you go.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_326
TranslationLabels.Text: (As the girls leave the office, Rebecca re-enters.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_327
TranslationLabels.Text: Rebecca, please show [NAME_1] to his room, and explain the details of the job to him.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_333
TranslationLabels.Text: You are free to use any of the facilities. But only when Miss Caine and the girls are not using them, of course.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_335
TranslationLabels.Text: You are free to help yourself to breakfast, lunch, and dinner in the kitchen.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_336
TranslationLabels.Text: Miss Caine and the girls will have their dinner in the dining room and are not to be disturbed.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_337
TranslationLabels.Text: (What, I'm not even allowed to join them for dinner?!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_339
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe she was just saying that so I would take the job?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_340
TranslationLabels.Text: Please use the rest of the day to pick up your belongings and take care of any unfinished business you may have.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_341
TranslationLabels.Text: Starting tomorrow, Miss Caine expects you be available whenever she calls.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_343
TranslationLabels.Text: Your first payment will be transferred to you tomorrow.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_345
TranslationLabels.Text: I have sent Miss Caines and the girls schedules to your phone. Make sure they arrive at their appointments on time and that you treat them with the utmost respect.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_352
TranslationLabels.Text: The likes of me?! What is that supposed to-

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_354
TranslationLabels.Text: So, while you stay under their roof, you will treat them with respect.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_359
TranslationLabels.Text: I will make sure to always treat them with the proper respect.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_10_363
TranslationLabels.Text: (At least I managed to calm her down a bit.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_11_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's go to my apartment first, by selecting it on the city tab on the map.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_4
TranslationLabels.Text: (The sooner I gather my things, the sooner Im out of here.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_5
TranslationLabels.Text: (But it shouldn't take me long...most of this stuff isnt even mine anyway.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_6
TranslationLabels.Text: (Not that I would want any of this junk...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_8
TranslationLabels.Text: (Anyway, Ill just grab my clothes and the few personal belongings I have left, so I can leave this place once and for all.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_11
TranslationLabels.Text: (Damn! That took me way longer than I thought!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_12
TranslationLabels.Text: (Anyway, lets head back to the mansion.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_13
TranslationLabels.Text: (Ooh, I like the sound of that!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_14
TranslationLabels.Text: (Who would have thought that Id be trading in this cramped little apartment for a fancy-ass mansion?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_12_15
TranslationLabels.Text: (I guess good things do come to those who wait...hehe!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_14_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (I don't see any reason to go back there.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_15_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (I better go pick her up, before she's late!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_16_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (I really need some coffee right now.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_16_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's use the map to go to the kitchen.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_17_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (I should wait here until Madeline returns.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_18_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (Huh, Rebecca? I wonder what she wants with me.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_18_4
TranslationLabels.Text: Miss Caine has asked me to invite you to join her and the girls for dinner.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_18_8
TranslationLabels.Text: Now, if you'll excuse me, I need to prepare dinner.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_18_9
TranslationLabels.Text: (It seems Madeline is finally warming up to me...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_18_10
TranslationLabels.Text: (It would probably be smart to accept her invitation.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (Time to find out what's behind that metal door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_5
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm, the corridor seems to split at the end.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_6
TranslationLabels.Text: (But there are also corridors to my left and right.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_12
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's start with that one and see where it leads...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_13
TranslationLabels.Text: (As you get closer to the ladder, you notice a hole in the wall.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_16
TranslationLabels.Text: (This is the backside of an air vent!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_17
TranslationLabels.Text: (It's too dark to see through it...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_18
TranslationLabels.Text: (But that must be the storage room Rebecca was talking about!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_19
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm...that's an odd place for an air vent.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_23
TranslationLabels.Text: (This ladder seems to go all the way up to the second floor.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_25
TranslationLabels.Text: (It seems to be a dead end.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_26
TranslationLabels.Text: (But there are two more air vents...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_32
TranslationLabels.Text: (Does that mean that the other corridors all lead to different rooms in the mansion?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_33
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm, Victoria's not in her room right now.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_36
TranslationLabels.Text: (Well, I'll have to find out if my theory about these corridors is correct at some point...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_39
TranslationLabels.Text: (So that would mean I have to take a left at the back of this corridor, to get to the bathroom?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_40
TranslationLabels.Text: (You walk to the end of the corridor...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_45
TranslationLabels.Text: (So that means the bathroom would have to be to the left...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_50
TranslationLabels.Text: (So this is how the blackmailer knew what I was doing?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_51
TranslationLabels.Text: (I can't believe I was being watched all this time...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_52
TranslationLabels.Text: (That means it has to be someone that knows about-)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_53
TranslationLabels.Text: (Oh! She's getting out of the bath...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_55
TranslationLabels.Text: (You have unlocked Victoria's naked paperdoll animation.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_56
TranslationLabels.Text: (I know I shouldn't be spying on her, but-)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_57
TranslationLabels.Text: (She leans over the bath to take out the stopper.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_58
TranslationLabels.Text: (-how can I not look at a body like that?!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_66
TranslationLabels.Text: (As she moves to the other side of the bathroom, you lose sight of her.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_72
TranslationLabels.Text: (Your eyes are drawn to the air vent.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_73
TranslationLabels.Text: (The blackmailer has probably been spying on me ever since I got here...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_74
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm, who else could know about the hidden corridors?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_77
TranslationLabels.Text: (The numpad in the utility closet looked old...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_78
TranslationLabels.Text: (But Madeline told me they moved here recently...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_79
TranslationLabels.Text: (So it's safe to assume that these corridors were put in by a previous owner.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_80
TranslationLabels.Text: (She also mentioned that my dad was the one who bought the house...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_81
TranslationLabels.Text: (In which case, the seller would have most likely informed him about the hidden corridors.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_82
TranslationLabels.Text: (And one of the keys was missing from the hidden compartment in the bookshelf...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_84
TranslationLabels.Text: (Although it doesn't explain how the blackmailer got the key from my dad...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_86
TranslationLabels.Text: (The seller didn't tell my dad about the hidden corridors, for some reason...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_87
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe they didn't know about them either?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_89
TranslationLabels.Text: (One of the girls found out about it just like I did?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_90
TranslationLabels.Text: (Which would not just explain the missing key, but the spying as well!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_94
TranslationLabels.Text: (Perhaps I'll by able to find out more, by doing a little spying myself...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_95
TranslationLabels.Text: (Or maybe, if I time it right, I can catch the blackmailer in the act, when they are coming out of the utlity closet!)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_97
TranslationLabels.Text: (I'm finally getting closer to finding out who has been blackmailing me.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_99
TranslationLabels.Text: (I'll make them pay for messing with me.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_19_107
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm, maybe I can investigate the hidden corridors a bit more?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_20_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's have a look at the map first.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_21_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's have a look at the mansion map first.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (Her tone implies that you are not welcome here.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_5
TranslationLabels.Text: What did I just tell you?!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_12
TranslationLabels.Text: Ah, [NAME_1]! Would you like to join us?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_13
TranslationLabels.Text: (Should I have dinner with the girls?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_14
TranslationLabels.Text: *Loud* Rebecca, could you bring one more plate, please?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_15
TranslationLabels.Text: You take your place at the dinner table...

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_16
TranslationLabels.Text: *Gasp* Oh my God, that cat video you showed me was so funny!

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_18
TranslationLabels.Text: I take it you had already finished your homework then?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_20
TranslationLabels.Text: Now what did I tell you about getting distracted?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_23
TranslationLabels.Text: I shouldn't have shown it to her while she was doing her homework, I'm sorry.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_25
TranslationLabels.Text: Still, Olivia should know better. Shouldnt you?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_27
TranslationLabels.Text: (She glances over at you and smiles.)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_29
TranslationLabels.Text: I will see you downstairs tonight.

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_34
TranslationLabels.Text: (I wonder what goes on down there...)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_36
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe I could try using the hidden tunnel to spy on them tonight?)

TranslationLabels.Label: c_1_100_39
TranslationLabels.Text: So, did you do your workout today, Annabelle?

TranslationLabels.Label: c_4_1000_3

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_140_2_1

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_140_3_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's just leave that where it is.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_140_3_2

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_140_4_1

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_140_8_1

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_300_5_2

TranslationLabels.Text: Hmm, Annabelle doesn't seem to be in her room...

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_250_2_1

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_250_2_3

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_250_7_1

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_250_9_1

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_250_10_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (I better get out of here before Rebecca catches me again...)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_250_10_4
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's just hope Madeline won't notice the book is missing.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Your attention is drawn to a peculiar section of one of the bookcases.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (There are seven narrow slots, but only two of them contain books.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_18
TranslationLabels.Text: (There seems to be some kind of hidden mechanism connected to these slots.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_19
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's see what this book is about.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_21
TranslationLabels.Text: (Gluttony, the vile harbinger of excess, doth poison the souls of the righteous and lead them astray from the path of temperance.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_22
TranslationLabels.Text: (It is a sin born of the flesh, a covetous desire that eclipses the spirit's purity, corrupting the very essence of the divine creation.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_23
TranslationLabels.Text: (O, ye faithful, beware the temptations that lay before you, for Gluttony in its relentless pursuit of gratification...)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_24
TranslationLabels.Text: (Damn, that sounds like something straight out of a religious cult initiation pamphlet.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_25
TranslationLabels.Text: (There's no way I'm going to read that.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_26
TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's just leave that where it belongs.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_28
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm...I wonder what happens when all slots are filled?)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_8_29
TranslationLabels.Text: (Maybe I should keep an eye out for the other books?)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_9_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (At first glance, it's just an old bookcase.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_9_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (But there more to it than meets the eye...)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_10_5
TranslationLabels.Text: (You slide the book of <highlight>Lust</highlight> into the corresponding slot.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_10_24
TranslationLabels.Text: (The other one seems to be missing...)

TranslationLabels.Text: (But I have no idea what they mean...)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_10_34
TranslationLabels.Text: (There must be some significance to these colors.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_10_37

TranslationLabels.Text: (Let's have another look at those colors.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_11_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (You press the hidden compartment and it pops open.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_11_9
TranslationLabels.Text: (There must be some significance to these colors.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_121_11_10
TranslationLabels.Text: (Alright, let's look around the mansion to see if there are any clues to these colors.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_1_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (There's seems to be some kind of metal door here!)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_1_6
TranslationLabels.Text: (I bet I can open that door, if I can figure out what the passcode is.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_3_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (Not something you would expect to see in a utility closet...)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_4_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (I'll leave the door locked for now.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_4_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (If you want to use the hidden corridors, just click the corresponding section off the mansion map.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_6_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (It's late, and I don't want to risk making any noise.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_450_6_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (I should come back here during the day.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_1_1
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm, that seems to be the wrong passcode.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_2
TranslationLabels.Text: (I can't believe I managed to crack the code!)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_3
TranslationLabels.Text: (The metal door slides up into the ceiling.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_7
TranslationLabels.Text: (I guess there's only one way to-)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_10
TranslationLabels.Text: (You quickly leave the utility closet and lock the door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_11
TranslationLabels.Text: What are you doing down here?

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_13
TranslationLabels.Text: Nothing, just...exploring the mansion a bit.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_18
TranslationLabels.Text: (Huh? What was she about to say?)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_20
TranslationLabels.Text: Yes, it's where Miss Caine keeps her...personal belongings and you are not to go in there under any circumstances.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_21
TranslationLabels.Text: (Oh, she is talking about the other door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_22
TranslationLabels.Text: Remember the terms of your contract.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_25
TranslationLabels.Text: (Could that be the "downstairs" they keep mentioning?)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_27
TranslationLabels.Text: Good. Then I suggest you stop snooping around here.

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_30
TranslationLabels.Text: (She is clearly waiting for you to leave.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_32
TranslationLabels.Text: (Hmm...I wonder what's in that "storage room" that got her so on edge?)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_33
TranslationLabels.Text: (Or maybe she knows about the metal door in the utility closet and doesn't want me near it?)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_34
TranslationLabels.Text: (Either way, I'm going to find out what's behind that door.)

TranslationLabels.Label: l_1_451_2_35
TranslationLabels.Text: (But I better wait until Rebecca finishes work.)

TranslationLabels.Label: i_8_1_2
